Thinking about the summer and what you are going to be doing?
Wondering how you are going to get all your service hours?
Do you enjoy working with younger kids?

Consider the Kids Institute Allies program or becoming a Problem-Based
Learning Watson and be a part of the summer program team!!!
Spend a week (or more) either teaching or group leading students from
3rd-10th grade. Earn 50 service hours per week.
Most importantly- Have fun!!!

We are looking for fun and dedicated students like you.

You must attend an Informational Meeting in order to receive the
application.